net.wequick.small

Class SoBundleLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wequick.small.BundleLauncher
      • net.wequick.small.SoBundleLauncher
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApkBundleLauncher, AssetBundleLauncher

    public abstract class SoBundleLauncher
extends BundleLauncher
    This class resolve the bundle file with the extension of ".so".

    All the bundle files are built in at application lib path (bundle.getBuiltinFile()).

    All the bundles can be upgraded after you download the patch file to bundle.getPatchFile() and call bundle.upgrade(). There are two primary implements of this class:

    • ApkBundleLauncher resolve the apk bundle
    • WebBundleLauncher resolve the native web bundle
